tment and National Security Agency.andP;  Data will beauthenticated electronically with the names of the transmitter and intendedreceiver.andM;* Edward Lieblein, director of computer software and systems for the DefenseDepartment, said DOD spends about $10 billion annually on mission-criticalsoftware and expects that to grow to 3 percent of the entire defense budget.andO;He said DOD's Software Technology for Adaptable, Reliable Systems willimprove software productivity and portability.andO;</TEXT></DOC>